  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nExtract emoji logic from StatusChatInput.qml. The code is tightly coupled with mentions logic.\r\n\r\nAlso define/implement the emojis overall behavior, currently emojis in the chat input are inserted only if typing the ascii alias and not the short name.\r\nThe Discord approach:\r\n\r\n- Detect emoji short name in chat input by showing a \"emoji suggestions\" popup on the second typed character after :\r\n- Detect both short name and ascii alias in chat history\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSee #7686 , #8464 ",
